Integrity is a [[Hardened Gentoo|Gentoo Hardened]] subproject aiming for the integration of system integrity technologies within Gentoo.

It currently focuses on the Integrity Measurement Architecture (or IMA) but does not want to limit its scope to this particular implementation.

